ur within dense (n > 10^3 cm^-3) environments, typical of\nmolecular clouds. The observations, therefore, primarily constrain the physical\nconditions -- metallicity, density, velocity fields -- of the gas within the\n(former) molecular cloud region surrounding the GRB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jun 2008 21:21:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
